            <p class="mb-5">To acquire a better connection with our community, we create an opportunity to do so with our live performance hours. Every Friday between 8 to 10 pm the stage is reserved for talented musicians. Every Sunday night we invite comedians to the stage to give our customers a fantastic Sunday’s night out!</p>
            <p class="mb-5">Our talented performers’ repertoires include cover versions of the best hits as well as their own compositions. We’re located at 655 Queen St. West, if you are nearby, come and grab your drink and enjoy the great shows.</p>
